data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: 1. Open one or multiple video files 2. Use MKV checkbox for easy blu-ray conversion 3. Create ffmpeg parameters then run parameters 4. This will create mkv files from smaller phone video files 5. Once done, open blu-ray tab and click to create blu-ray 6. Select all the mkv files you want on your disc, choose order 7. Use your favorite disc burning program to burn BDMV to disc or create image file 8. Enjoy your home movies on physical media
